Package org.openlca.core.matrix

Class FlowIndex

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.core.matrix.FlowIndex
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<IndexFlow>, MatrixIndex<IndexFlow>, Copyable<MatrixIndex<IndexFlow>>
public abstract class FlowIndex extends Object implements MatrixIndex<IndexFlow>
The row index $\mathit{Idx}_B$ of the intervention matrix $\mathbf{B}$. It maps the (elementary) flows $\mathit{F}$ of the processes in the product system to the $k$ rows of $\mathbf{B}$.

$$\mathit{Idx}_B: \mathit{F} \mapsto [0 \dots k-1]$$
